<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <title>Welcome to Custom Layout - Set Up Your Password</title>
  </head>

  <body>
    <p>Dear <%= name %>,</p>

    <p>
      Welcome to Custom Layout! Your account has been successfully created.
      Please use the link below to set up your password and log into your
      account. This link is valid for 24 hours.
    </p>

    <p>Your user name is your email address of <%=user?.email%>.</p>

    <p><a href="<%= resetLink %>"> <%= resetLink %> </a></p>

    <p>
      If you did not request this account creation, please disregard this email.
    </p>

    <p>Sincerely,</p>
    <p>Insight Flow Team</p>
  </body>
</html>
